	 hair down (or strings loose) in No Strings Attached—a hilarious\\\, adult
	s improv puppet show. After a long day entertaining the kids\\\, these pup
	pets are ready to play—singing bawdy songs\\\, cracking jokes\\\, and gett
	ing up to all kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call the sho
	ts with your suggestions! \\nDon’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show at 
	Pike Place Market. It’s puppets\\\, it’s improv\\\, and it’s guaranteed to
